iamente in inglese. Al momento sembra irreperibile.","like_count":4,"author_id":"UCDwYznhe7UOr8BtqfhAQWtg","author":"@lupash","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/b_CTN8pvMToylxtKIW2sHdOhWdP0rRsbN--GvtEH1juf1Us5TS87VeZtASbHV_TBBUGmpORF=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_is_verified":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@lupash","is_favorited":false,"_time_text":"6 years ago","timestamp":1588118400,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"UgwU5hHHE7psTdSq_Mp4AaABAg.8pj752KT3eG9WTXI5mVlXF","parent":"UgwU5hHHE7psTdSq_Mp4AaABAg","text":"Finalmente si è scoperto. Occhio agli ultimi post sulla Falange Benson","like_count":5,"author_id":"UC2RSyR31Ayu1IkbltBm62rA","author":"@Christian-NaitSirC","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_m4d5K8CLicSOEx3_P891s2FW6laPKsAzB9pUsPG1hkz-M=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_is_verified":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@Christian-NaitSirC","is_favorited":false,"_time_text":"4 years ago","timestamp":1651190400,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"Ugw1vgsIn8LETtzHeol4AaABAg","parent":"root","text":"Io l'ho sempre detto Richard è il nostro big fish. Ai posteri l'ardua sentenza.","like_count":11,"author_id":"UCu8NVbCnScM7sd8ujZUS48A","author":"@steogrillhouse","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_mzbqTrnfC6nrq3kOQJeAiiH53cdGYcLqMsPS1DAn2FYQ=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_is_verified":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@steogrillhouse","is_favorited":false,"_time_text":"7 years ago","timestamp":1556496000,"is_pinned":false}]